cast.overview: A young boy named Luke and his grandmother go on vacation only to discover their hotel is hosting an international witch convention, where the Grand High Witch is unveiling her master plan to turn all children into mice. Will Luke fall victim to the witches' plot before he can stop them?
cast.title: The Witches

details.biography:
Annabel Brooks is a British actress who has appeared on television and in films since the 1980s. Brooks is also the owner of Avenue Property Luxury Home Rentals & Escapes.

Her first on-screen role came in 1987 when she appeared as Eliza in Nightflyers. She has since appeared in productions including A Handful of Dust, The Witches and Last Run.
details.name: Annabel Brooks
